Package Downloads

Daniel Turek

Data downloaded from CRAN, the Comprehensive R Archive Network, 24 February, 2021.

Green lines show LOWESS [1] smoothed curve.

suppressMessages(library(cranlogs))
suppressMessages(library(gplots))

df <- data.frame(
    pkgs = c('nimble', 'basicMCMCplots', 'MATA', 'nimbleSCR', 'nimbleSMC', 'BayesNSGP'),
    ymax = c(200, 80, 50, 30, 30, 40)
)

from <- '2018-01-01'

downloads <- cran_downloads(df$pkgs, from = from, to = Sys.Date())

for(i in 1:nrow(df)) {
    count <- downloads[downloads$package == df$pkgs[i], ]$count
    date <- downloads[downloads$package == df$pkgs[i], ]$date
    plot(count ~ date,
         main = df$pkgs[i], ylim = c(0, df$ymax[i]),
         type = 'l', xlab = 'Date', ylab = 'Daily Downloads')
    ind <- min(which(count > 0)) : length(count)
    smoothed <- gplots::lowess(count[ind] ~ as.numeric(date[ind]))
    lines(smoothed$x, smoothed$y, col = 'green', lwd = 2)
}

[1] Cleveland, W. S. (1979). Robust locally weighted regression and smoothing scatterplots. Journal of the American Statistical Association, 74(368), 829-836.
